{"tid":1132173,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"蓋清覺得依單嘢炒唔炒得起？","createTime":"2019-04-30T06:32:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T08:14:14.000Z","uid":175032,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"33d8f6f0103d6a5ac9442e714f8e7985d83f1b56","tid":1132173,"uid":175032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T06:32:50.000Z","msg":"(星島日報報道)日本一個非牟利組織周一推出裝有「平成空氣」的罐頭，裏面還放了一個五日圓硬幣及祝福，每個要價一千零八十日圓（約七十六港元）。由於在平成年代接近尾聲時具有紀念價值，預計販售約六百個，吸引不少遊客購買。岐阜縣關市有一個地方名叫「平成」，名叫「日本平成村」的組織趕在日本年號即將從平成改為令和之前，販售裝有「平成空氣」的罐頭。一名到此地觀光的日本女性說，因為覺得很罕見，所以就買下來，還表示「重量很輕呢」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/detail/1993423-國際-日「平成空氣」罐頭76元一罐\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2Fdetail%2F1993423-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E6%97%A5%E3%80%8C%E5%B9%B3%E6%88%90%E7%A9%BA%E6%B0%A3%E3%80%8D%E7%BD%90%E9%A0%AD76%E5%85%83%E4%B8%80%E7%BD%90&d=jZUVzsr%2BlXwf2hbAbvJm1Y%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=704251c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2Fdetail%2F1993423-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E6%97%A5%E3%80%8C%E5%B9%B3%E6%88%90%E7%A9%BA%E6%B0%A3%E3%80%8D%E7%BD%90%E9%A0%AD76%E5%85%83%E4%B8%80%E7%BD%90&h=bee3eacc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/detail/1993423-國際-日「平成空氣」罐頭76元一罐</a>"},{"pid":"3aac61a2a3254d7ff7f05bcf9a258e997f98ed05","tid":1132173,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T06:34:47.000Z","msg":"咁能ON9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57c072e1c01898e6fbf1f4eefe064a0c34d34eba","tid":1132173,"uid":45189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T06:45:10.000Z","msg":"加拿大公司 Vitality Air 就將當地的空氣放到網店發售，並且更成功吸引到不少中國消費者選購。"},{"pid":"dcead636c50fdf9a123e67b8a1f8a1e2782ae74e","tid":1132173,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20